My baby was denied access to Paris and a bunch of other places in the pandemic, missed opportunities, money and just being able to move around like a regular human being, something allot of us take for granted. It was even times we would show up to the airport with all our bags packed, flights booked , just to be told she cant travel , it was beyond heartbreaking. So the last slide was her moment of clarity, finally realizing all that shit is finally over. Deeper than just a trip to paris, she got her freedom back, and everything she missed out on coming back tenfold. Amen.
